; Source: Computer Science Logo Style, Volume 2 Chapter 13, Fourier Series Plotter.
; Source URL: https://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~bh/v2ch13/fourie.html
; Modeled deterministic fixture: plot a small sampled sine-wave curve as a
; headless turtle trace suitable for CI.

clearscreen
setpc 6
setpensize 1
penup
setxy -6 0
pendown
repeat 7 [setxy sum -6 repcount product 4 sin product repcount 30]
